# Staged copies for the Railway openemr Dockerfile build context are
# regenerated by scripts/deploy-openemr.sh from the canonical sources
# (interface/modules/custom_modules/... and src/Common/Session/...).
# NOT git-ignored: Railway's CLI respects .gitignore when uploading the
# build context, so ignored paths never reach the build daemon. Don't
# `git add` them by accident — stage files individually as usual.
